@in_dg94
I know it's a 650MB file. I wouldn't be bitching if he didn't have 720p in the file titles. Just because the frame height is 720 pixels doesn't mean you can advertise it as being 720p or classify it as highres. It's like he took a 480p video and upscaled it so the frame height was 720 pixels. This upload (and all of his other ones) should NOT be in the Highres section. There should be an upscale section for shit like this. 

@YIFY Would it KILL YOU to keep the audio quality? That was what really pissed me off more than anything. I can deal with shit quality video, but when I can't hear what is being fucking SAID, THAT's when I rage. Fuck your uploads.
